/8085932/ed-sheeran-divide-nielsen-music-top-album-2017|title=Ed Sheeran's 'Divide' Is Nielsen Music's Top Album of 2017 in U.S.|work=Billboard|last=Caulfield|first=Keith|date=January 3, 2018|accessdate=January 15, 2018}}</ref>|accessdate=April 14, 2018}}\n|-\n{{Certification Table Bottom|streaming=true}}\n\n==Release history==\n{| class=\"wikitable plainrowheaders\"\n! Region\n! Date\n! Format\n! Label\n! {{abbr|Ref.|References}}\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| Various{{efn|Release as a [[promotional single]].}}\n| May 8, 2017\n| [[Music download|Digital download]]\n| rowspan=\"4\"| {{hlist|[[Kidinakorner]]|[[Interscope Records|Interscope]]}}\n| <ref name=\"Spotify\"/>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" rowspan=\"2\"| United Kingdom\n| October 6, 2017\n| [[Contemporary hit radio]]\n| <ref name=\"BBC\">{{cite web|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/radio1/playlist|title=BBC Radio 1 Playlist|publisher=[[BBC]]|accessdate=October 14, 2017}}</ref>\n|-\n| October 20, 2017\n| Digital download\n| <ref>{{cite web|last=Stickler|first=Jon|title=Imagine Dragons Tickets For March Arena Shows On Sale 9am Today|url=https://www.stereoboard.com/content/view/211018/9|website=Stereoboard|accessdate=October 14, 2017|date=September 22, 2017}}</ref>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| United States\n| November 14, 2017\n| [[Adult album alternative]] radio\n| <ref>{{cite web|url=http://playiga.com/genre/aaa/|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20171031220225/http://playiga.com/genre/aaa/|title=Music Meeting for October 31|publisher=Play IGA|archive-date=October 31, 2017}}</ref>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| Germany\n| November 17, 2017\n| [[CD Single]]\n| {{hlist|Interscope|[[Universal Music Group|Universal]]}}\n| <ref>{{cite web|title=Whatever It Takes (2-Track) - Imagine Dragons: Amazon.de: Music|url=https://www.amazon.de/gp/product/B076L8DG5K/ref=s9u_simh_gw_i2?ie=UTF8&pd_rd_i=B076L8DG5K&pd_rd_r=e4ac7f92-bc13-11e7-a008-71ec069f688d&pd_rd_w=fOT51&pd_rd_wg=ZQdOh&pf_rd_m=A3JWKAKR8XB7XF&pf_rd_s=&pf_rd_r=CZPPKHGEVX77VQZAMF5X&pf_rd_t=36701&pf_