halam (film)|Arunachalam]]'' || Ponnambalam || Tamil ||\n|-\n| ''[[Vallal]]'' || Uncle of Annam || Tamil ||\n|-\n| ''[[Adimai Changili]]'' || || Tamil ||\n|-\n| ''[[Janakiraman]]'' || || Tamil ||\n|-\n| ''[[Lady Commissioner]]'' || || Kannada ||\n|-\n|rowspan=\"6\"| 1998 || ''[[Pavitra Prema]]'' || M.L.A. Rayudu || Telugu ||\n|-\n| ''[[Dharma (1998 film)|Dharma]]'' || Khan || Tamil ||\n|-\n| ''[[Simmarasi]]'' || Police inspector || Tamil ||\n|-\n| ''[[Urimai Por]]'' || Marthandan || Tamil ||\n|-\n| ''[[Veeram Vilanja Mannu]]'' || Police inspector || Tamil ||\n|-\n| ''[[Vettu Onnu Thundu Rendu]]'' || || Tamil ||\n|-\n|rowspan=\"11\"| 1999 || ''[[Thulladha Manamum Thullum]]'' || || Tamil ||\n|-\n| ''[[Chinna Durai (1999 film)|Chinna Durai]]'' || || Tamil ||\n|-\n| ''[[Ullathai Killathe]]'' || || Tamil ||\n|-\n| ''[[Rajasthan (film)|Rajasthan]]'' || || Tamil ||\n|-\n| ''[[Kummi Paattu]]'' || || Tamil ||\n|-\n| ''[[Kanave Kalaiyadhe]]'' || || Tamil ||\n|-\n| ''[[Amarkalam]]'' || Aasairaj || Tamil ||\n|-\n| ''[[Kannupada Poguthaiya]]'' || || Tamil ||\n|-\n| ''[[Kanmani Unakkaga]]'' || || Tamil ||\n|-\n| ''[[Azhagarsamy]]'' || || Tamil ||\n|-\n| ''[[Mudhal Etcharikkai]]'' || Ponnambalam || Tamil ||\n|-\n|rowspan=\"11\"| 2000 || ''[[Thirunelveli (film)|Thirunelveli]]'' || || Tamil ||\n|-\n| ''[[Mugavaree]]'' || || Tamil ||\n|-\n| ''[[Thai Poranthachu]]'' || Dharma || Tamil ||\n|-\n| ''[[Sudhandhiram]]'' || || Tamil ||\n|-\n| ''[[Vallarasu]]'' || Manikkam || Tamil ||\n|-\n| ''[[Pennin Manathai Thottu]]'' || || Tamil ||\n|-\n| ''[[Maayi]]'' || || Tamil ||\n|-\n| ''[[Krodh (film)|Krodh]]'' || || Hindi ||\n|-\n| ''[[Nuvvu Vastavani]]'' || || Telugu ||\n|-\n| ''[[Choosoddaam Randi]]'' || Tiger Dharma || Telugu ||\n|-\n| ''[[The Warrant]]'' || || Malayalam ||\n|-\n|rowspan=\"9\"| 2001 || ''[[Looty]]'' ||  || Tamil ||\n|-\n| ''[[En Purushan Kuzhandhai Maadhiri]]'' || Santhamoorthy || Tamil ||\n|-\n| ''[[Eduruleni Manishi]]'' || || Telugu ||\n|-\n| ''[[Sri Raja Rajeshwari]]'' ||  